291
00:16:23,397 --> 00:16:24,562
<i>Tout de suite,</i>

292
00:16:24,822 --> 00:16:27,278
<i>le marathon des Kroft Superstars.</i>

293
00:16:28,517 --> 00:16:30,526
<i>Joy et moi sommes rentrés
2 jours plus tard</i>

294
00:16:30,852 --> 00:16:32,633
